Sentencas: The research of ceria-based electrolyte is of great significance for application of medium or low temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: The Influence of Doped Iron Oxide on the Performance of Ceria-Based Solid Electrolyte

Sentencas: In this paper, Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-delta (CGO) and CGO doped with 2.0 nnol% FeO1.333 (2Fe-CGO) were synthesized by low-temperature combustion method, and the effects of doped iron oxide on density and conductivity were studied.
Titulo: The Influence of Doped Iron Oxide on the Performance of Ceria-Based Solid Electrolyte

Sentencas: The experimental results indicated that the relative density of 2Fe-CGO increased within a certain temperature range due to the occurrence of viscous flow sintering.
Titulo: The Influence of Doped Iron Oxide on the Performance of Ceria-Based Solid Electrolyte

Sentencas: It was found that Fe3O4 could clear SiO2 impurities in the grain boundary, which can greatly enhance the conductivity of 2Fe-CGO.
Titulo: The Influence of Doped Iron Oxide on the Performance of Ceria-Based Solid Electrolyte

Sentencas: The conductivity of 2Fe-CGO was two orders of magnitude larger than CGO's when the test temperature was 250 degrees C.
Titulo: The Influence of Doped Iron Oxide on the Performance of Ceria-Based Solid Electrolyte
